contentrichtext.text: '''Luis Rodriguez''' may refer to: *[[Luis Manuel Rodríguez]] (1937–1996), Cuban boxer *[[Luis J. Rodriguez]] (born 1954), American author *[[Luis Rodríguez (volleyball)|Luis Rodríguez]] (born 1969), Puerto Rican volleyball player *[[Luis Rodríguez (baseball)|Luis Orlando Rodríguez]] (born 1980), Venezuelan baseball player *[[Luis Rodríguez (footballer)|Luis Ricardo Rodríguez]] (born 1982), Guatemalan football player *[[Luis Antonio Rodríguez]] (born 1985), Argentine football player *[[Luis Alfonso Rodríguez|Luis Rodríguez Alanís]] (born 1991), Mexican football player *Luis Rodríguez (born 1992), member of the Costa Rican team in the [[2009 FIFA U-17 World Cup squads|2009 FIFA under-17 world cup]] *Luis Rodríguez, referee in the [[2009–10 CONCACAF Champions League Group Stage]] *[[Luis Rodríguez (producer)|Luis Rodríguez Salazar]], Spanish record producer based in Germany *Luis Orlando Rodríguez, Cuban journalist, politician and interior minister and the first commentator of [[Radio Rebelde]] == Fictional == *Luis Rodriguez, a [[List of characters in Sesame Street|human character on ''Sesame Street'']] ==See also== *[[José Luis Rodríguez (disambiguation)]] {{hndis|Rodriguez, Luis}}
